CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 3, 1957, pg. A15, reads: "SMCS Delegates - Some of the delegates attending the School of Missions and Christian Service at Warren Methodist Church, July 22-26, were caught be The Courier photographer at recess. This leadership training institute is sponsored by the Women's Society of Christian Service of the Washington Conference. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Women, delegates attending School of Missions and Christian Service, gathered on steps of Warren Methodist Church, Hill District
